this is how I prep material to make leaves and petals for my plant inspired work ❤️‍🔥 From a cylinder to a patty , stretched down to a ribbon as long as my wingspan and then I break it down into sections & each individual component ! Lots of hours go into prep work yall ! ❤️‍🔥 Please note I’m clearly a glass blower and not a videographer 😅 thanks for watching ! #gnarlacarla

Hey hey everybody! Mic check one two one two , is this thing on? Figured I’d pop in to say hello ! I’m still out here making glass 👩🏻‍🏭✨ been focusing energy towards other things besides posting on Insta. Honestly after 20 years of working with glass and a handful of tough years as an independent artist it’s been refreshing to work on simpler things , and step away from the headies . I do continue to make pipes and always open for orders or customs but the market is changing and it is nice to switch it up!  Pictured here is the current most popular item I make, my wall hanging bud vases (great for propagating plants too )! Comment below or send smoke signals if you’re seeing this post ! 💖💖💖💖 much love & thank you for your continuous support #gnarlacarla
